{"tid":155190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Inception]一人一個發夢發緊夢","createTime":"2017-03-13T22:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T12:40:18.000Z","uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eea66e9bb3e635d181206989f871568dc5dc597e","tid":155190,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:03:38.000Z","msg":"個夢嘅情境actually 喺我自己間房, 而我係訓緊喺我張床上面. <br />\n我突然間醒咗,我發覺自己起唔到身, 好似比鬼壓咁樣. <br />\n事關因為我平時我係開住收音機訓教, 但係夢入面我仍然聽到收音機.<br />\n然後我費盡九牛二虎之力終於都爬咗起身啦, 我望望周圍, 但係唯獨我睇唔到自己兩臂,不過我係摸到feel 到自己兩隻手仲係到.<br />\n跟住我即刻跑去阿媽間房搵阿媽,發覺自己點叫都好不過都係無聲. 然後我試下去開掣, 點知明明係見到個掣, 不過點㩒都㩒唔到. 又係攪左好耐終於比我㩒到.<br />\n一㩒落去我番番去我張床上面, 以為自己醒左啦. 點知個夢又loop多一次. 不過依一次無之前一次咁辛苦, 最後又係去㩒燈掣.<br />\n一㩒又係番番自己張床, 不過今次真係醒, 即刻摸下自己兩隻手係唔係到.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為個夢真係逼真,所以醒番果時仲驚緊.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d378250afd623801420d1f3712707004e1a7c3","tid":155190,"uid":3103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:07:01.000Z","msg":"其實你仲係夢入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe4ba52f49b77709ce6f2b44a1ab38385495d45","tid":155190,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你仲係夢入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2753e7278603d6996f46238592f09518788db023","tid":155190,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bbbdd6bef97ac76cbe3a9f2bd4228621d8be59","tid":155190,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c05d288a6789eab51f7e0266f2201c68506e78c","tid":155190,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"