rown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cc186ce52ec4f6757bf78ea5bf5981d5ab9311","tid":155190,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發夢夢見自己係個綠色既海入面游水<br />\n係海入面同海豚玩見到藍鯨仲有好大條既魔鬼魚<br />\n游得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知突然醒左仲沖左出房同屋企人講發左個好正既夢 點知自己突然真係醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住同屋企人講發左個夢中夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個夢真係好靚搞到有啲唔想醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係你唔會好驚咩"},{"pid":"3502ec71d3089e45e2a7b6c27e63fc377f4cdbe7","tid":155190,"uid":2869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發夢夢見自己係個綠色既海入面游水<br />\n係海入面同海豚玩見到藍鯨仲有好大條既魔鬼魚<br />\n游得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知突然醒左仲沖左出房同屋企人講發左個好正既夢 點知自己突然真係醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住同屋企人講發左個夢中夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個夢真係好靚搞到有啲唔想醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係你唔會好驚咩</blockquote><br />\n夢入面閉氣閉到好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9f2e110cb5b39d6b12807a7fa3c180555e9bd6","tid":155190,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>發夢夢見自己係個綠色既海入面游水<br />\n係海入面同海豚玩見到藍鯨仲有好大條既魔鬼魚<br />\n游得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知突然醒左仲沖左出房同屋企人講發左個好正既夢 點知自己突然真係醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住同屋企人講發左個夢中夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個夢真係好靚搞到有啲唔